# Third-Party Skills Registry

**Reference:** DSM_0.2 §23.1 (Third-Party Skill Governance)
**Status:** Local-only, gitignored per-instance. Lists third-party skills installed
on this DSM installation (global `~/.claude/skills/` or project-level `.claude/skills/`).

## Installed Skills

| Skill | Source | Version | Scope | Purpose | Conflicts | Register-sensitive |
|-------|--------|---------|-------|---------|-----------|--------------------|

## Maintenance

Update this file when installing, removing, or updating a third-party skill.
See DSM_0.2 §23.2 (Evaluation Gate for Skill Installation) for the pre-install
review checklist. Register-sensitive skills (e.g., humanizer) require a runtime
context block on every invocation per §23.4.
